TextEng: Me find shield. You name be on it.
Text: 나 방패 찾았어. 너 이름 있어.

TextEng: I found this shield with your name on it.
You takes me 50 gold and gets you arm back.
Text: 너 나 금화 50개 주면 팔 돌려줘.

TextEng: No thanks.
Sure.
Here, take this 50 gold and get your arm back.
No thanks.
Sure.
No, you keeps you gold. You needs it.
Text: 아니, 너 금 가져. 너 필요해.

TextEng: No, you keep your gold. You need it.
Me take you gold.
I'll be taking the gold.
"Goodbye."
"What happen to you arm."
"What happened to your arm?"
<StartCheck>[Intimidate]</Start> "Tell me what happen or maybe you lose other arm."
Text: <StartCheck>[위협]</Start> "무슨 일 있었는지 말해 안 그러면 다른 팔도 없어."

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Intimidate]</Start> "Tell me what happened or maybe you'll lose that other arm."
Text: <StartCheck>[위협]</Start> "무슨 일이 있었는지 말해요. 안 그러면 남은 팔도 잃을지 몰라요."

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Bluff]</Start> "Me hear customer say you lose it 'cause you be coward."
Text: <StartCheck>[허세]</Start> "나 손님이 말하는 거 들었어. 너 겁쟁이라서 팔 잃었다고."

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Bluff]</Start> "I heard some customers say you lost it because you're a coward."
<StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> "Me want be you friend. Please tell me."
Text: <StartCheck>[설득]</Start> "나 너 친구 되고 싶어. 제발 말해줘."

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> "I'd like to be your friend. Please tell me."
"Me no need you life story. Hurry up."
Text: "나 너 인생 이야기 필요 없어. 빨리 말해."

TextEng: "I don't need your life story. Hurry up."
"What girl that be?"
"What girl is that?"
"That still no tell me where you arm go."
"That still doesn't tell me how you lost your arm."
Text: "아직도 팔을 어떻게 잃었는지 말 안 했잖아요."

TextEng: "Go on."
"At least you survive."
"At least you survived."
"So how you end up here?"
"So how did you end up working here?"
"Me think me no allowed."
"I thought I wasn't allowed."
"Yes, please."
"Me allowed to leave."
"I'm allowed to leave."
<StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> "Durnan be me friend; him no mind."
Text: <StartCheck>[설득]</Start> "더난 내 친구야. 걔 신경 안 써."

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> "Durnan's my friend; he won't mind."
Text: <StartCheck>[설득]</Start> "더난은 제 친구예요. 신경 안 쓸 거예요."

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Intimidate]</Start> "You let me out, or me tell Durnan you forget what him tell you 'bout me."
Text: <StartCheck>[위협]</Start> "나 내보내. 안 그러면 더난한테 이를 거야."

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Intimidate]</Start> "You let me out, or I'll tell Durnan you forgot his instructions."
Text: <StartCheck>[위협]</Start> "내보내 주세요. 안 그러면 더난한테 지시 사항 잊었다고 말할게요."

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Bluff]</Start> "You forget. No worry, me no tell nobody you forget."
Text: <StartCheck>[허세]</Start> "너 잊었어. 걱정 마, 나 아무한테도 안 말해."

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Bluff]</Start> "You must have forgotten. Don't worry, I won't tell anybody you forgot."
Text: <StartCheck>[허세]</Start> "잊으셨나 보네요. 걱정 마세요, 아무한테도 안 말할게요."
